      "author": "lumargh",
      "description": "## What's new\n\n### Preserve structure setting\nA new **Preserve structure** toggle is available in Settings → File Filter. When enabled, ancestor headers of matching blocks are shown when filtering a page — even if those headers don't contain the search term. Disabled by default; existing behaviour is unchanged when off.\n\n### Nested list fix\nIntermediate list items that don't match the search term are now correctly hidden. Matching items that are deeply nested still surface, with non-matching ancestors silently collapsed out of view.",
