      "author": "github-actions[bot]",
      "description": "## Added\n- **Filter in Live Preview / Source mode** — paragraph filtering now works while editing, not just in reading mode. Non-matching paragraphs collapse into a clickable ellipsis, matching text is highlighted, and the line your cursor is on stays visible so you can keep editing in place.\n- **Per-item list filtering** — bullet and numbered lists filter item by item instead of as a single block.\n- **Filter inside embedded files** (`![[page]]`) — in both reading and editing modes; an embed whose file has no match collapses entirely.\n\n## Changed\n- The inline paragraph editor has been split out into a separate **Paragraph Editor** plugin. File Filter is now focused solely on filtering.\n",
